#  DynXSec 

DynXSec is a lightweight **Security Information and Event Management (SIEM)** system designed for **real-time monitoring, alerting, and case management**.


##  Features

###  Security Dashboard
###  Log Management
###  Alert Engine
###  Case Management


##  Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/DynXSec.git
cd DynXSec
```

### 2. Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Run Backend Server

```bash
cd server
python app.py
```

### 4. Open Frontend

Open `index.html` in your browser


